name: Amy Zill
text: Garlic crust was very flavorful. Though it was a bit flimsy and thin for a hand tossed pizza. Ordered delivery. Ordered 2 blue cheese dip cups. Got 2 ranch cups. I hate ranch! I drove to pizza hut to get my blue cheese cups. I rarely order delivery for this reason. Thought I'd give it another chance.

name: Kevin Shockney
text: This place needs a interior/exterior facelift for starters because it looks like it's straight out of the early 90's. Also, it seems like no matter how slow it is inside, it takes entirely too long to get our food. Once the food arrives then it's good as usual. If I could give this place 0 stars I would. Never visiting again.

name: Steven G

text: The waitress was so nice, she was the only person working at the time. The food is delicious, especially the stuffed crust. She talked about how the place is suffering, really hoping it doesn't get shut down!

name: Dallas Kinard
text: My wife is the Pizza hut fan but I can enjoy it on occasion. This location is very chill and laid back so that's a plus. It's almost never busy! The food was decent and the service was good.
